ze:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;">THE PRESIDENT:&nbsp; That's =
me!&nbsp; (Applause.)&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-si=
