<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-si=
ze:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;">THE PRESIDENT:&nbsp; Thank y=
ou, sir.&nbsp; I appreciate it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-si=
ze:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-si=
ze:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;">All right.&nbsp; Let me do s=
ome business here.&nbsp; Let me begin by recognizing some of the guests who=
 are here.&nbsp; Your mayor, Karen Weaver, is here.&nbsp; (Applause.)&nbsp;
 I know Governor Rick Snyder is here.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNoSpacing" style=3D"text-indent:.5in"><span style=3D"font-si=
